Text:
Love these uploads.

Thanks, man.

 PS... you might wanna sign up for a few other mailers: Catherine's, Fashion Bug, Cato.... there's one more I can't think of right now.

Torrid's probably what you're thinking of.  They do send me stuff, but most of it doesn't have models on it.

Fashion bug is good but their models are more typical bra-ad models, unlike the Lane Bryant ladies.  I'm not sure about Cathrines or cato.
Thanks for the comment, too ... It's nice to know that these are appreciated since they are a bit of work.
These are always fantastic! Please keep posting them, and I will keep seeding them.
Sorry for the late comment, but these Lane Bryant uploads are the best on the 'net.  Thanks for putting in the time, and I look forward to more in the future.  Thanks!
